name: Extimacy 2 Hypervigilated Societies
description: The most valuable thing for an ordinary citizen is to remain hidden from the IA Artificial Intelligence. The word "extimacy" is an invention of Lacan. The ultimate is what is closest, the most interior, without ceasing to be exterior. It is a paradoxical formulation. The term "extimacy" is built on "intimacy". NFT artwork.
